First Bank of Nigeria’s FBN Capital Appoints Research and Sales Heads

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-31T15:05:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/first-bank-of-nigeria-s-fbn-capital-appoints-research-and-sales-heads.html
First Bank of Nigeria Plc (FIRSTBAN) ’s
investment banking and asset management unit, FBN Capital, has
appointed research and institutional sales heads.  Bunmi Asaolu will head equity research while Gregory
Kronsten will oversee macroeconomic and fixed income research,
the Lagos-based bank said in an e-mailed statement today. Wale
Adebayo will be the head of institutional sales.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  